  • Packages that use net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base

    net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base
    Base classes for field and row mapper implementations, and supporting classes.

    Base classes for repositories and schema generators.
    net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.service.base
    Base classes for application services.
  • Classes in net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base used by net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base 
    Class and Description
    ClassFieldMapper
    A mapper for any specific field of a given class.
    ColumnType
    A description of the SQL-level properties of a given field.
    DesMapper
    Functional interface for field deserializer functions.
    EnumRowMapper
    A row mapper for tables which reflect enums - writing is as normal, but reading is id-only and materializes as the preexisting instance by ordinal.
    FieldMapperTransform
    A transformation to apply to a field mapper.
    InvertibleRowMapper
    An extension of the RowMapper interface to include information sufficient to bind a class to a row or a part thereof and also allow for inserting instances
    InvertibleRowMapperBase
    A row mapper.
    JoiningRowMapper
    A mapper for objects represented over multiple tables.
    Mapper
    A type-safe mapper for a specific field of a given class.
    MapperAndJoin
    Defines a join between two mapped types, a parent and contained type, on a single field of each
    MapperAndJoin.DeleteStyle
    Ways to handle deletions across a join
    MapperAndJoin.GetterState
    State and function for retrieving one or more contained instances from a parent instance
    MapperAndJoin.GetterState.State 
    MapperAndJoin.InsertStyle
    Ways to handle insertions across a join
    MappingException
    Unified exception for various things that can go wrong while mapping fields.
    PsSetter
    Sets a value into a prepared statement.
    PsSetterFactory
    Implementations (such as included defaults) can create type-safe value setters for PreparedStatement fields.
    PsSetterFactory.SetterPsOrdinalValue
    Functional interface extracted from various PreparedStatement setX methods.
    RowMapperTransform
    Specifies a transform to apply to a row mapper.
    RsGetter
    Functional interface for methods which extract values from ResultSets
    RsGetterFactory
    Implementations (such as included defaults) can create type-safe getters for ResultSet fields.
    RsGetterFactory.GetterRsFieldName
    Functional interface extrapolated from ResultSet getX methods.
    SerMapper
    Functional interface for field serializer functions.
    SqlOp
    Some SQL comparison operations.
